productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Betha has one of these. She works as a teacher and she says it looks wide.
My co-worker Tyron has one of these. He says it looks stout.
I tried to shred it but got watermelon all over it.
My co-worker Aurthur has one of these. He says it looks white.
heard about this on bouyon radio, decided to give it a try.
